France_Volontaire and the Volunteering_Space for Vietnam and Laos invite you to join our event , the French_Volunteer_Day .
This event will take place at AFD/EFEO gardens in Ho_Chi_Minh_City ( 113 Hai_Ba_Trung , Ben_Nghe , D1 ) .
Come to join us and discover how the international NGO and local NPO create good conditions for a sustainable development of Vietnam !
Conference , fair and photo exhibition are in the program !
